{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2e45ba209c","title":"要根治淮河","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"07ca20eecb","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"a0e6245a72","index":1,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"2e45ba209c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenji6","name":"毛泽东文集第六卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji6.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"58e56be327","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指华东军政委员会1950年8月28日转报中共苏北区委对治淮的意见给周恩来的电报。苏北区党委意见的第三项是：“如今年即行导准，则势必要动员苏北党政军民全部力量，苏北今年整个工作方针要重新考虑，既定的土改、复员等工作部署必须改变，这在我们今年工作上转弯是有困难的；且治淮技术上、人力组织上、思想动员上及河床搬家及其他物资条件准备等等，均感仓促，对下年农业生产及治沂均受很大影响。如果中央为晚救皖北水灾，要苏北改变整个工作方针，服从整个导淮计划，我们亦当竭力克服困难，完成治准大计。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8551b27deb","type":"title","text":"要根治准河","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"58e56be327","type":"subtitle","text":"周：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"b62ba94849","type":"paragraph","text":"除目前防救外，须考虑根治办法，现在开始准备，秋起即组织大规模导淮工程，期以一年完成导淮，免去明年水患。请邀集有关人员讨论（一）目前防救、（二）根本导淮两问题。如何，请的办。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"0259d5c4bd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"954c70ed14","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十日周：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"931dee814b","type":"paragraph","text":"请令水利部限日作出导淮计划，送我一阅。此计划八月份务须作好，由政务院通过，秋初即开始动工。如何，望的办。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"35054bdf69","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"2dd34f1335","type":"paragraph","text":"八月五日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"2bd60d8315","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"4aa87fb734","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"06cc21bc27","type":"paragraph","text":"此电第三项有关改变苏北工作计划问题，请加注意。导淮必苏、皖、豫三省同时动手，三省党委的工作计划，均须以此为中心，并早日告诉他们","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"af2fc1849c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"7f139eaaaf","type":"paragraph","text":"八月三十一日","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"a8327053f7","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"ac82b69837","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"b5c3af6073","type":"paragraph","text":"现已九月底，治淮开工期不宜久延，请督促早日勘测，早日做好计划，早日开工","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"bad933578a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"ddb973e042","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十一日","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c"}],"page":{"id":"7c3a7ae92b","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2e45ba209c","start":42,"end":43}},"wenji6":{"comments":[{"id":"35f5286a30","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c","index":2,"part_index":13,"offset":2,"text":"指华东军政委员会一九五○年八月二十八日转报中共苏北区委对治淮的意见给周恩来的电报。苏北区党委意见的第三项是：“如今年即行导淮，则势必要动员苏北党政军民全部力量，苏北今年整个工作方针要重新考虑，既定的土改、复员等工作部署必须改变，这在我们今年工作上转弯是有困难的；且治淮技术上、人力组织上、思想动员上及河床搬家，及其他物资条件准备等等，均感仓促，对下年农业生产及治沂均受很大影响。如果中央为挽救皖北水灾，要苏北改变整个工作方针，服从整个导淮计划，我们亦当竭力克服困难，完成治淮大计。”"},{"id":"51a2e73012","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c","index":1,"part_index":2,"offset":1,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"5e41c05b8f","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据手稿刊印。"}],"contents":[{"id":"07f3f3d993","type":"title","text":"要根治淮河","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"1c63e45322","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":19,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"35f5286a30","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"3ed013c07b","type":"paragraph","text":"请令水利部限日作出导淮计划，送我一阅。此计划八月份务须作好，由政务院通过，秋初即开始动工。如何，望酌办。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"42c9caa6f7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":14,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"51a2e73012","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"7afe346780","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"8221026072","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":17,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"8ce1599867","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"8cfbfcfb89","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十一日","index":20,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"9c9071a5c0","type":"paragraph","text":"此电第三项有关改变苏北工作计划问题，请加注意。导淮必苏、皖、豫三省同时动手，三省党委的工作计划，均须以此为中心，并早日告诉他们。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"9da80b113c","type":"paragraph","text":"除目前防救外，须考虑根治办法，现在开始准备，秋起即组织大规模导淮工程，期以一年完成导淮，免去明年水患。请邀集有关人员讨论（一）目前防救、（二）根本导淮两问题。如何，请酌办。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"a97e1db6f2","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"b870369415","type":"paragraph","text":"现已九月底，治淮开工期不宜久延，请督促早日勘测，早日做好计划，早日开工。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"c4affde698","type":"paragraph","text":"八月三十一日","index":15,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"c85032e5b9","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"cdae6b7c46","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"cfcb287b6a","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"d2e0252a91","type":"paragraph","text":"八月五日","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"ea234cb505","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":16,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"},{"id":"fbccab6e68","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c"}],"page":{"id":"64f97ca348","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"2e45ba209c","start":99,"end":100}}}},"__N_SSG":true}